---
title: "Outbox Pattern — Subida de Archivo (FSD-UC-002 / FSD-UC-007)"
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor E as Estudiante
    participant FS as file-service
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant OB as outbox_events
    participant RL as MessageRelayService<br/>(Polling cada 2s)
    participant RMQ as RabbitMQ<br/>simoncloud.simondrop.events
    participant NS as notification-service

    E->>FS: POST /drops/:id/upload (buffer + JWT)
    Note over FS: uploadAndHash() → SHA256Hash VO

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over FS,OB: prisma.$transaction — ATÓMICO
        FS->>PG: UPDATE files SET sha256Hash, status='COMPLETED'
        FS->>OB: INSERT outbox_events {eventType:'ArchivoSubidoIntegrationEvent', published:false}
        PG-->>FS: COMMIT
    end

    FS-->>E: {fileId, sha256Hash, publicUrl}

    Note over RL: @Interval(2000ms) — Polling Publisher
    RL->>OB: SELECT WHERE published=false ORDER BY createdAt LIMIT 10

    alt channel.publish() = true (buffer disponible)
        RL->>RMQ: publish(exchange, 'archivo.subido', payload, persistent:true)
        RL->>OB: UPDATE SET published=true, publishedAt=NOW()
        Note over RL: at-least-once garantizado
    else channel.publish() = false (back-pressure)
        RL->>RL: break — reintento en siguiente ciclo
        Note over RL: evento queda published=false
    end

    RMQ->>NS: Consume ArchivoSubidoIntegrationEvent

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over NS: Deduplicación por eventId (Módulo 5)
        NS->>PG: INSERT processed_events ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING
    end

    NS-->>E: Email/Push "Nueva entrega confirmada"
